msgid ""
"Dolphin showing KIO GDrive in lower right, and Falkon browsing Google Drive "
"in upper left."
msgstr ""
"Dolphin zobrazuje KIO GDrive vpravo dole a Falkon prehliadajúci Google Drive "
"vpravo hore."
